name: MORNING RUSH at JAPAN'S BUSIEST AIRPORT! Tokyo Haneda Plane Spotting 羽田空港
description:
Tokyo's Haneda Airport is the busiest airport in Japan, serving mainly domestic traffic with a mix of some international visitors too.

Like most Japanese airports, it also has three fantastic observation decks, one on the roof of each terminal. This video was filmed over a morning and into the afternoon one day in May 2023 from the three different terminals.

Hope you all enjoy!
